Maintainer: Arnaud Kyheng <Arnaud.Kyheng@free.fr>
Uploaders: Daniel Baumann <daniel@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev, dialog, gettext, guile-1.8-dev, libadns1-dev, libcurl4-gnutls-dev, libextractor-dev (>= 0.5.18), libgcrypt11-dev, libglade2-dev, libgmp3-dev, libgtk2.0-dev, libmicrohttpd-dev, libltdl3-dev, libmysqlclient15-dev, libncurses5-dev, libsqlite3-dev, libxml2-dev, po-debconf, zlib1g-dev
